{"tid":2460702,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實非洲有乜撚嘢問題，講咗幾十年都未解決","createTime":"2021-03-25T04:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T17:27:10.000Z","uid":282619,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e37db94574bd9fbd107f8e45b665c3dc206da42a","tid":2460702,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"我細個睇電視已經話非洲有問題，有飢荒呀，小朋友無飯食呀，有疾病呀，然後就叫我哋捐錢，屌，捐咗十幾二十年，有無變過，又好似無變過，電視一路繼續叫人捐<br />\n授人以魚，不如授之予漁，其實係咪做唔到？因為非洲啲地唔得定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e753942e90528248878ff4d1d8ee4b515fe0df","tid":2460702,"uid":387826,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZSaXYSGNWhGkq8sgppQ2UqSn3dSogAuQc6nmXhaAvnhQ?filename=NKDPhSv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKDPhSv.png&h=504ec034&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQn8uXmnkTKqxmYAvaitcqEJaQgnwo72dkmCwCVeVNcwu?filename=P9XXrLR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP9XXrLR.png&h=aad7d102&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRt7QvnwraSF5koKkSDX1zUND87Sn2hUcsEYxRp9erFuD?filename=o37kpxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo37kpxw.jpg&h=3da7bccd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQfsLLmfaUK9JGvqTfiEMtJuBBYbQ7ih3Ws49XwHxzkay?filename=j4pCrLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4pCrLR.jpg&h=7a6dc9c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6edd436143e1df7311eb47fb38d4f8e34d960b1a","tid":2460702,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:10:28.000Z","msg":"因為你叫班仆街爛坦咪撚生絕育會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a